{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body>\n\n<p>發佈時間：21:41 2026-04-22 HKT</p>\n<img alt=\"「雷神太保」輕鬆捧盃\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl_square/0fd7d6ca17a95b7376ecff2482941d0b/2026-04/r5_6.jpg\"/>\n<p>今晚快活谷第五場四班千二米西洋會盃，繼第四場的「銳目」之後，騎師潘頓在今場夥拍黎昭昇馬房的「雷神太保」輕鬆擊敗對手，贏得在港首場頭馬，潘頓在騎師王積分表上以三十分領先。</p>\n<p>今晚潘頓在第五場憑黎廄的「雷神太保」出戰四班谷草千二米，順利贏馬捧走西洋會挑戰盃，而他贏馬捧盃後，更將獎盃交給女馬迷打卡留念，認真寵粉。</p>\n<p>練馬師黎昭昇贏「雷神太保」取得今季第十八場頭馬，賽後練者說：「『雷神太保』在港跑了二十一場仍然未開齋，但馬兒跑短途賽尚算準繩，多次有接近的走勢，今場潘頓沿途守好位，直路貼欄形勢有利，順利取勝，我十分感謝馬主給予耐性，畢竟此馬來港跑了逾二十場才交出頭馬，希望馬兒今場取勝後，增強馬匹的信心，開竅後會越跑越好。」</p>\n<h2>按下圖睇更多相片：</h2>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/13e79e1a5553a1c1e493e41529ef3f46/2026-04/2c5eb0ef-91d3-44dc-a9e8-a6e9346150b3.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/dc8ae81f5e480ad67b5f30e3f258ebd9/2026-04/07caad17-ca18-4bd2-ac85-790fea8c76c9.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/1c5d836215b9daf0d5b9d6edca14305c/2026-04/9c9c102e-4756-42fb-8507-989eb1fe75ac.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/0e9e3ead17af168cf3d12853d391ac76/2026-04/017b606e-4904-48b7-87ee-a07b68fbdd7e.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/7ae415baac9b42f937ea81758cac161d/2026-04/21c8e167-c721-4fbe-829e-b52006cd905f.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/a5f8d835a08bbda3e77b197b37c1b285/2026-04/33dc92d9-fad0-468f-92eb-fe7db66721bb.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/b7bb14473504b75a27473e65f3db0271/2026-04/0044d110-2368-4fe7-8401-a54e0ecf658f.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/fb1ada29e92aac428e31d35dee68a384/2026-04/71ae37bb-a48f-4ce9-bd9b-03d8acc507aa.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/348ddeb2ccd5d253c4c829e0a90a88fd/2026-04/5965693b-50ae-499a-9df3-e88a45901646.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/08f654d0543dfecd574ed2a474686349/2026-04/a77ea223-45d2-4cb2-9134-b6aaeecc6d6e.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/89f44c402d4a006d0d6d94281379d47b/2026-04/bbf17b50-81d8-4063-b329-2e908f63ea29.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/7224d72c1d9f8922e0f762737e6fd7eb/2026-04/bf4e7541-3c24-4376-adb4-42ca05288842.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/e1a38173b7e10002b200d2e8df35de53/2026-04/c997a3cd-1515-44fb-a8eb-ca50100701d0.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/f89996bc2b2a97b1d91863929616939e/2026-04/ccd288c2-1542-481b-8914-1da6dae26310.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/a908664ff6be58e6f269dedfd206da8e/2026-04/db7c15c5-1d0f-467f-9673-24b3ed4b76e8.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/099ff154bb11089e2e7da37de9a6c981/2026-04/f6a972b6-61ca-4dc7-91d5-940245534bcf.jpg\"/>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T14:13:36.220745+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":344,"images":17,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}